      "Request Safety Screen"
    ],
    "h2": [
      "Thank you for requesting a safety screen!"
    ],
    "h3": []
  },
  "paragraphs": [
    "Keeping your family safe is our top priority. We make it easy to get a safety screen for a past or current model. First find your model and serial number, then submit the form below or contact your local dealer.",
    "Manufactured before January 1, 2003",
    "You will receive a safety screen free. Just supply the serial number and model number. You only pay for shipping ($15 USD/$25 Canada).",
    "Manufactured between January 1, 2003 and December 31, 2014",
    "If your safety screen is damaged or missing, a replacement is available for $99 USD/$130 Canada. Shipping is free. Then send the form below.",
    "Manufactured after January 1, 2015",
    "You can purchase a safety screen through your local Heat & Glo dealer, then pick it up at your convenience.",
